[ { _id: 0, avgprice: 326.6875 } ]

products> db.product_details.aggregate([{$group:{_id:0,minprice:{$min:'$price'}}}])

10. Develop an aggregation pipeline to illustrate Text search on Catalog data
collection.
test> use movies
switched to db movies
movies> db.movies.aggregate(
[
{ $match: { $text: { $search: "Action" } } },
{$sort: {title:1}},
{ $project: { title: 1, _id: 0} }
]
)
[ { title: 'Bang Bang' }, { title: 'Fanaa' }, { title: 'Robin Hood' } ]
